زين كاش هي محفظة هاتف نقال مرخصة من البنك المركزي العراقي . من خلالها يمكنك دفع فواتيرك, حجز تذاكر طيران, تحويل اموال, اعادة تعبئة رصيد هاتفك النقال , تسوق الكترونيا وغيرها الكثير بسرعة , سهولة وامان.
 
حساب مالي رقمي
توفر زين كاش امكانية فتح حساب رقمي وبدون اي اجور فتح او متطلبات حد ادنى للرصيد. تستطيع ايداع وسحب الاموال من خلال الاف نقاط البيع المنتشرة في عموم العراق وكذلك تستطيع التحقق من رصيدك من خلال هاتفك النقال.
 
ارسال / استلام الدفعات
ارسل واستلم دفعات اموال من الزبائن او الاصدقاء. كما يمكنك ترك ملاحظة مع كل تحويل وممكن تتضمن رموز تعبيرية (emojis)
 
شحن الرصيد الكترونيا
اشحن رصيد هاتفك النقال او اي هاتف نقال تابع لخطوط الدفع المسبق لزين العراق او ادفع فواتير الخطوط الاجلة الدفع لزين العراق.
 
شراء بطاقة ماستر كارد
اشتري بطاقة ماستر كارد الالكترونية واستلمها فورا للتسوق الكترونيا عبر ملايين المواقع الالكترونية
 
احجز تذاكر طيران وغرف فنادق
احجز تذاكر رحلتك واختر غرفة الفندق بصورة مباشرة , مع زين كاش ستحصل على افضل الاسعار.
 
التسوق الكترونيا
تسوق المنتجات الاكثر مبيعا من الازياء الرجالية والنسائية, هواتف  النقال و الاجهزة الالكترونية, ادوات منزلية , اكسسوارات , مجوهرات, تجهيزات اطفال وغيرها
 
اضافة اموال الى محفظة زين كاش الخاصة بك
اضف اموال الى محفظتك عبر ايداعها في احد مراكزنا ال3000 والمنتشرة في عموم العراق. يمكنك معرفة اقرب مركز متوفر من خلال تطبيق زين كاش
لمواكبة كل ماهو جديد من زين كاش يرجى متابعة موقعنا الالكتروني  www.zaincash.iq

تطبيق الكتروني يهدف إلى تسهيل عملية دفع الأقساط الشهرية للمواطنين المقترضين في صندوق الإسكان العراقي. يتميز التطبيق بواجهة بسيطة وسهلة الاستخدام، مما يتيح للمستخدمين إدارة مدفوعاتهم بكل يسر وسرعة.

First Iraqi Bank is Iraq’s first-ever completely mobile bank. 

First Iraqi Bank’s completely digital onboarding process is fully compliant with KYC (Know Your Customer) guidelines and legal requirements. You can open a bank account in under 5 minutes and enjoy a wide range of services provided by the app. All you need is your ID card or a Passport. You can get onboarded even faster if you are a KRG (Kurdish Regional Government) employee. First Iraqi Bank app features include: 

-Deposit. Quickly and conveniently deposit your cash using a wide network of merchants all around Iraq. You can do this by simply showing your unique QR code to the merchant. The balance will be updated instantaneously.

-Withdrawal. Quickly and conveniently withdraw cash using a wide network of merchants all around Iraq. You can do this by simply scanning a QR code provided by the merchant. Your balance will be updated instantaneously.

-QuickPay. Pay for goods and services by simply scanning the QR code generated by the merchants. It will only take seconds!

-Money conversion. Do you want to store and spend your money in different currencies? With First Iraqi Bank you can easily convert your money between IQD, USD, and EUR.
 
-Money transfers. Perform Peer-to-Peer money transfers to other First Iraq Bank account holders. They will get the money within seconds! First Iraqi Bank also allows you to make local and international transfers to other banks.

-Balance and transactions. Never lose track of your finances! You can always view the details of your transactions and see the history of changes in your balance.

-Service Store. With First Iraqi Bank you can quickly purchase vouchers and gift cards from more than 100 different providers (e.g., Careem, Netflix, etc.) using your current balance. They will appear in the app’s wallet after the purchase, from where you can also share them with your friends and family.

-Money boxes. Saving up for a new car or even a house? Take advantage of our money boxes feature! It allows you to save your money in separate spaces away from your main balance.

-Find branches and stores. Quickly find our nearest branch office of First Iraqi Bank, where we will be happy to serve you. Looking for the nearest merchant to make a deposit or withdrawal? You can conveniently find them on the map.

-Spending limit. Take control of your monthly spending by setting a spending limit. If your next transaction goes over the limit you will be notified.

-Cash delivery. Don’t have a possibility to reach our network of merchants to deposit or  withdraw money? Don’t worry, we have your back! First Iraqi Bank app allows you to track, and schedule cash withdrawal deliveries and cash deposit collections.

In pursuit of our mission to be the preferred Non-Banking Financial Services solution provider by providing the most comprehensive and innovative bouquet of services, along with our vision to be the forerunner and leader in Non-Banking payment Services and to become a part of the customers' everyday lives, we concentrate on and directly target the financial needs and issues of the customers to pioneer groundbreaking and advanced set of services that address all the needs. The Central Bank of Iraq (CBI) licenses AsiaPay after complying fully with the requirements of CBI pursuant to Iraq Electronic Payment Service No (3) of 2014, Anti-Money Laundering (AML) and Counter Terrorist Finance (CTF) no 39 of 2015. 

            Company Strategy:
           - Vision: To be the number one choice for any mobile financial transactions in the country.
           - Mission: Delivering the most advanced financial services for our clients throughout Iraq.
           - Goal: Make AsiaPay every day’s choice.

            

Core Values:
We are a team that strives for improvement, never stops working, and uses cutting-edge technology to give our clients the best customer service possible.
To meet the needs of every class, AsiaPay offers three different types of wallets.
Lite wallet is a fast short-termed wallet. The threshold of the lite wallet is 2,000,000 million IQD for three months either per day or per the activation period, which is 90 days. Lite wallet holders must transfer the wallet to Standard wallet after three months because the wallet will be suspended. 
Standard Wallet can be obtained by visiting one of the AsiaPay agents throughout Iraq after the completion of registration procedures (Know Your Pay Customer). The threshold of the Standard wallet is 2,000,000 IQD daily and 10,000,000 IQD monthly. The wallet will be active for an unlimited period subject to the terms and conditions of AsiaPay. 

Premium Wallet is a type of wallet that has been designed for employers, merchants, main dealers, high earners, and VIPs. The threshold is defined by the AsiaPay on a case-by-case basis in accordance with Central Bank of Iraq instructions. This wallet can be obtained by visiting AsiaPay’s main dealers only.
